rten.jpg\" linkedin=\"http://au.linkedin.com/in/mortenblomfeldt/\" mail=\"morten@bluecloudaustralia.com.au\"][/member][/one_fourth] [one_half_last]\r\n\r\n<strong>Background</strong>\r\n\r\nBlueCloud was founded in August 2011 and was launched commercially in March 2012. Prior to this, the early versions of BlueCloud were created as an in house solution for Antoine\'s call centre in Sydney at the time. Stuck between expensive and complex premise-based solutions from Cisco, Avaya and others on one side and incapable standalone diallers on the other, Antoine decided that he would benefit greatly from creating something better. Along the way he could also see the strong commercial viability of the BlueCloud Technology, based on the number of requests he got from other operators.\r\n\r\nMorten joined him full time in June 2012 and together they are now proud to offer the first professional self-service telephony and productivity solution, ready to be launched internationally.\r\n\r\nThe core BlueCloud team is based in Pyrmont, Sydney, with resellers also appointed for all major Australian states as well as the Philippines and Singapore.\r\n\r\nLook out for exciting new developments on the BlueCloud platform very soon.\r\n\r\n[/one_half_last]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','About Us','','publish','open','open','','about-us','','','2013-06-18 00:07:37','2013-06-18 00:07:37','',0,'http://localhost/blueCloudWord/?page_id=50',0,'page','',0),(1227,5,'2013-06-06 12:14:13','2013-06-06 12:14:13','[one_fourth][member name=\"Antoine Nookadu\" role=\"CEO\"  img=\"antoine.png\" linkedin=\"http://au.linkedin.com/in/antoinenookadu/\" mail=\"antoine@bluecloudaustralia.com.au\"]My awesome super longdsadaddsdadd and powerful description of a person[/member][/one_fourth]\r\n\r\n[one_fourth][member name=\"John Doe\" role=\"Web Developer\" url=\"http://example.com\" img=\"http://mintithemes.com/nopic.png\" twitter=\"http://twitter.com\" facebook=\"http://facebook.com\" skype=\"http://skype.co