,'open','open','','56-revision','','','2013-05-09 05:02:22','2013-05-09 05:02:22','',56,'http://localhost/blueCloudWord/56-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(184,5,'2013-06-19 21:54:37','2013-06-19 11:54:37','[toggle title=\"What is your service level guarantee?\" open=\"true or false\" ]\nWe have a multi-location infrastructure set up. Routing protocols are in place for redundancy and automatic switching. However, just like any internet based service we are reliant on availability of internet connections, and are some times at the mercy of natural disasters. We have an agreed uptime guarantee which is clearly stated in our User Agreement. You can rest assured that our support team will attend to any hardware related matter immediately should an incident arise.[/toggle]\n\n[toggle title=\"Do you support multi-site set up?\" open=\"true or false\" ]\nBlueCloud is the ideal solution for multi-site set up and for home-based staff. Through BlueCloud’s Live Monitor, you are able to monitor and manage staff remotely from any device. Our online BlueCloud Chat functionality is also a powerful way to keep the entire team connected.[/toggle]\n\n[toggle title=\"I already have a in-house dialler – can I still trial the system?\" open=\"true or false\" ]\nIt’s always a good thing that you are already using a dialer, as you are familiar with this functionality. However, there are some notable limitations with such technology. Your Agents and Administrators will enjoy using BlueCloud – the simplicity and fluidity of the system is addictive. Make sure you get their feedback![/toggle]\n\n[toggle title=\"Can I make changes to active campaigns while agents are making calls?\" open=\"true or false\" ]\nAbsolutely. This makes it possible to make changes at any time during the campaign – even when you are on the road and can only access internet through your phone. Changes will be effected immediately through our powerful back end.[/toggle]\n\n[toggle title=\"How quickly can I get started?\" open=\"true or false\" ]\nAs BlueCloud does not require any special infrastructure or equipment on your end, this can be done very quickly. Depending on the number of agents you wish to enable, set-up can be done as early as the same day if required.[/toggle]\n\n[toggle title=\"How will you charge me?\" open=\"true or false\" ]\nBlueCloud is a pay-as-you-go service with no contracts and no up front hardware investments required. You will pay a small set up fee to get started and will then pay in advance per seat/month. Payment can be made using a credit card (VISA, MasterCard or Amex) or via direct debit. You will be notified by email when credit is low so you can top up your account.[/toggle]\n\n[toggle title=\"What do I need to do to get started?\" open=\"true or false\" ]\nBlueCloud is a cloud based application, hence there is no need for any special hardware on your end. All that is required is an internet enabled computer with a headset for each agent – you don’t even need your telephone system anymore. Does not get much simpler than that.[/toggle]\n\n[toggle title=\"Why BlueCloud? I already have a system in place.\" open=\"true or false\" ]\nAsk yourself these questions….\n<ul>\n	<li><em>Does my system allow me to set up and run a new campaign in less than 15 minutes?</em></li>\n	<li><em>Could I be spending too much on technology</em></li>\n	<li><em>Am I in a Contract? What if have a slow month/year?</em></li>\n	<li><em>Do I pay for Administrator access?</em></li>\n	<li><em>Do I pay for support? Service Agreements?</em></li>\n	<li><em>Do I pay extra for basic features such as recording?</em></li>\n	<li><em>Do I have instant email features as well as video email?</em></li>\n	<li><em>Does my system give me access the cheapest VoIP price plans in the industry?</em></li>\n	<li><em>Am I able to add home based agents and track them the same way as the office based agents?</em></li>\n</ul>\nWe think it may be time for you to review your technology. Call us on 1800 2