56','','BC_overview','','inherit','closed','open','','bc_overview','','','2013-06-18 03:56:56','2013-06-18 03:56:56','',1377,'http://localhost:8080/restorewp/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/BC_overview.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(1377,5,'2013-06-18 04:00:56','2013-06-18 04:00:56','[responsive]<a href=\"http://localhost:8080/restorewp/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/BC_Infra.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1490\" alt=\"BC_Infra\" src=\"http://localhost:8080/restorewp/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/BC_Infra-1024x672.png\" width=\"960\" height=\"630\" /></a>[/responsive]\r\n\r\n[one_half]\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em><strong>BlueCloud  is a solution created for non-techies and allows you to get started immediately, as no special hardware is required on your end.</strong></em></p>\r\n<strong>Agents</strong> connect via a desktop or laptop to the BlueCloud server and calls are made directly through their computer. No desktop phones are involved. We offer multiple VoIP providers on our end to make the calls, and you may also bring your own favourite provider.\r\n\r\n[/one_half]\r\n\r\n[one_half_last]\r\n\r\n<strong>Administrators</strong> can access their control panel from any device, including smart phones and tablets. From their control panel they can create new campaigns, monitor existing ones and change campaign settings at any time. Through the control panel they can also access reports, call recordings etc. from anywhere.\r\n\r\n<strong>External stakeholders</strong> (clients, other departments, senior management) can be given their own login credentials in order to access reports and other information specified by the the above administrators. This way, BlueCloud clients save significant time on reporting, while providing everyone with up to date information about the ongoing campaigns.\r\n\r\n[/one_half_last]\r\n\r\n[box style=\"1\"]\r\n\r\n[one_third]\r\n\r\n<strong>Security</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong></strong>BlueCloud runs on the most secure and scalable cloud platform, Amazon AWS,  available in 8 extremely well connected locations worldwide (including Sydney, Singapore and Tokyo in the Asia Pacific region). This cloud platform is already in use by clients with the most stringent security requirements, such as Nasdaq.\r\n\r\nIn addition BlueCloud applies the latest security protocols to ensure that your data remains secure on our platform. BlueCloud clients enjoy the full redundancy and backups that give them all the confidence they need and more time to focus on their business.\r\n\r\n[video type=\"youtube\" id=\"jOhbTAU4OPI\"]\r\n\r\n[/one_third]\r\n\r\n[one_third]\r\n\r\n<strong>Simplicity</strong>\r\n\r\nSimplicity is much more than a work in the BlueCloud camp. We create simple solutions which allow our clients to spend far less time on training and implementation projects and any other solution. Agents will only need a quick 10 minutes run-through, while administrators are trained and ready over a half-day workshop.\r\n\r\nWe have deliberately created a very different solution, which does not require any techies at all to implement, monitor or manage the solution from your end.\r\n\r\n[responsive]<a href=\"http://localhost:8080/restorewp/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/bic-biro1-e1370786126389.jpg\"><img alt=\"bic biro\" src=\"http://localhost:8080/restorewp/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/bic-biro1-e1370786126389.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"335\" /></a>[/responsive]\r\n\r\n[/one_third]\r\n\r\n[one_third_last]\r\n\r\n<strong>Flexibility/Scalability</strong>\r\n\r\n[responsive]<a href=\"http://localhost:8080/restorewp/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/BC_Devices3.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1464\" alt=\"BC_Devices3\" src=\"http://localhost:8080/restorewp/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/BC_Devices3-300x274.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"274\" /></a>[/responsive]\r\n\r\nAs a BlueCloud client you will find yourself with more flexibility than ever, as you only pay for the number of seats you requi