xpertise</strong>\r\nAcquiring a dialer also means that someone needs to know how to use it. Ideally there should be a few people who know this, even in small to mid-sized organisations. In addition to training cost, this normally also means increasing the headcount and added cost for the company.<strong></strong>\r\n\r\nBut wait…this article was supposed to talk about the benefits of predictive dialers, not about the barriers. The reality is that many companies can still justify the cost and the additional headcount due to the huge increases in productivity. BlueCloud is now here to take this even further.\r\n\r\nAs we have already demonstrated to a lot of small and mid-sized teams, our technology provides a way to get all benefits of a predictive dialler WITHOUT any of the problems/barriers mentioned above. How?<strong></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Cost</strong>\r\nFirst of all, there is no capital spent up front, and just a small subscription fee paid each month. The subscription fee has no contracts, and BlueCloud therefore remains flexible to your changing needs. Pay only for what you use.<strong></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Simplicity</strong>\r\nWe have removed the complexity of using this type of tools and have made it possible for anyone with enough skills configure their Facebook profile to use BlueCloud comfortably.\r\n\r\n<strong>No hardware</strong>\r\nNo specialists required. All you need is an internet connected computer with a headset for your agents. You don’t even need desktop phones!<strong></strong>\r\n\r\nAnd now, finally, the big question: What are these 3 key benefits of a predictive dialer?\r\n\r\n<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>1. Increase number of connected calls</strong></span>\r\nIt is common to increase the number of connected calls in a day by more than 70%. No more time wasted waiting for unconnected calls and answering machines (yes we automatically detect this with BlueCloud). That is one massive jump in productivity!<strong></strong>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>2. Get in charge of your metrics</strong></span>\r\nAgain, a good dialer will give you access to all key campaign metrics whenever you need them. How many calls have been made, how many connected, how many per outcome (e.g. how many sales), etc. Best of all, you can get this per agent or per team or filter the results according to your requirements. This is how to keep the client happy and also how to keep making your team better.<strong></strong>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>3. Get control over callbacks</strong></span>\r\nA good dialer (not all) will give you a full overview over callbacks agreed by the agents, nicely sorted by date and time.\r\n\r\nGood luck and don’t forget to ask your technology provider some tough questions. Can at least say that we are ready to answer.\r\n\r\n</div>','Top 3 benefits of a predictive dialler (dialer)','','inherit','closed','open','','1432-revision-3','','','2013-06-19 09:18:16','2013-06-18 23:18:16','',1432,'http://localhost:8080/restorewp/1432-revision-3/',0,'revision','',0),(1443,5,'2013-06-19 09:27:37','2013-06-18 23:27:37','<a href=\"https://www.google.com.au/url?sa=i&amp;rct=j&amp;q=&amp;esrc=s&amp;source=images&amp;cd=&amp;cad=rja&amp;docid=Ovl2vAd_3UGXeM&amp;tbnid=kwc811pXaMCcRM:&amp;ved=&amp;url=http%3A%2F%2Fsovibrantopinion8.blogspot.com%2F2012%2F12%2Fdesign-classic-no-52-bic-cristal.html&amp;ei=EtQ9Ud2YMKudmQW8joGYDQ&amp;psig=AFQjCNFh7qSss1CNS4aKzQukZ5A1fg12jQ&amp;ust=1363092883130786\">“Simplicity is the ultimate sophistication”</a>\r\n\r\n- LEONARDO DA VINCI\r\n\r\n[responsive]<a href=\"http://localhost:8080/restorewp/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/Microwave.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1441\" alt=\"Microwave\" src=\"http://localhost:8080/restorewp/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/Microwave-267x300.png\" width=\"267\" height=\"300\" /></a>[/responsive]\r\n\r\nDo you still remember the first microwave o