platform. BlueCloud clients enjoy the full redundancy and backups that give them all the confidence they need and more time to focus on their business.\r\n\r\n[video type=\"youtube\" id=\"jOhbTAU4OPI\"]\r\n\r\n[/one_third]\r\n\r\n[one_third]\r\n\r\n<strong>Simplicity</strong>\r\n\r\nSimplicity is much more than a work in the BlueCloud camp. We create simple solutions which allow our clients to spend far less time on training and implementation projects and any other solution. Agents will only need a quick 10 minutes run-through, while administrators are trained and ready over a half-day workshop.\r\n\r\nWe have deliberately created a very different solution, which does not require any techies at all to implement, monitor or manage the solution from your end.\r\n\r\n[responsive]<a href=\"http://localhost:8080/restorewp/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/bic-biro1-e1370786126389.jpg\"><img alt=\"bic biro\" src=\"http://localhost:8080/restorewp/wp-content/uploads/2013/06/bic-biro1-e1370786126389.jpg\" width=\"500\" height=\"335\" /></a>[/responsive]\r\n\r\n[/one_third]\r\n\r\n[one_third_last]\r\n\r\n<strong>Flexibility/Scalability</strong>\r\n\r\nAs a BlueCloud client you will find yourself with more flexibility than ever, as you only pay for the number of seats you require for a particular month. Whole team shut down for a slow period? No problem - no bills from BlueCloud. Need to hire 15 casual workers to handle an extra peak? We have your extra seats ready instantly. Your cost is under control with our price plan.\r\n\r\nWe are also able to customise your setup according to your needs (e.g. Have your agents in the Philippines make calls through our servers in Australia for optimal voice quality). We challenge any other provider to match this flexibility. We are also able to accommodate any form of setup on your end. Multi-country/facility setups are no match for BlueCloud.\r\n\r\n[/one_third_last]\r\n\r\n[/box]','Overview','','inherit','closed','open','','1377-revision-24',