ns-pricing/\">Find out how&gt;&gt;</a>\r\n\r\n[/one_third] [one_third]\r\n<h3>A Plan for Everyone</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">[responsive] <a href=\"http://localhost:8080/restorewp/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/BC_Tiers.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1466\" alt=\"BC_Tiers\" src=\"http://localhost:8080/restorewp/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/BC_Tiers-300x217.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"217\" /></a>[/responsive]</p>\r\nBlueCloud offers three simple plans to choose from. We have the right solution for you - even if your requirements change overnight. <a title=\"Plans &amp; Pricing\" href=\"http://localhost:8080/restorewp/plans-pricing/\">Learn more about our plans &gt;&gt;</a> [/one_third] [one_third_last]\r\n<h3>Who is it for?</h3>\r\n[responsive]<a href=\"http://localhost:8080/restorewp/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/People_City_2.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1468\" alt=\"People_City_2\" src=\"http://localhost:8080/restorewp/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/People_City_2-300x248.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"248\" /></a>[/responsive]\r\n\r\nBlueCloud is specifically designed for small to mid sized call centres (outsourced, in-house sales teams, lead generation, market research, fundraising etc.) Do you make a lot of outbound calls in your organisation? <a title=\"Contact Us\" href=\"http://localhost:8080/restorewp/contact-us/\">Contact us now &gt;&gt;</a>[/one_third_last]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','The first self-service telephony and productivity solution for call centres...and beyond','','inherit','closed','open','','23-revision-139','','','2013-06-19 21:47:55','2013-06-19 11:47:55','',23,'http://localhost:8080/restorewp/23-revision-139/',0,'revision','',0),(1472,5,'2013-06-18 01:48:32','2013-06-18 01:48:32','[toggle title=\"What is your service level guarantee?\" open=\"true or false\" ]\r\nWe have a multi-location infrastructure set up. Routing protocols are in place for redundancy and automatic switching. However, just like any internet based service we are reliant on availability of internet connections, and are some times at the mercy of natural disasters. We have an agreed uptime guarantee which is clearly stated in our User Agreement. You can rest assured that our support team will attend to any hardware related matter immediately should an incident arise.[/toggle]\r\n\r\n[toggle title=\"Do you support multi-site set up?\" open=\"true or false\" ]\r\nBlueCloud is the ideal solution for multi-site set up and for home-based staff. Through BlueCloud’s Live Monitor, you are able to monitor and manage staff remotely from any device. Our online BlueCloud Chat functionality is also a powerful way to keep the entire team connected.[/toggle]\r\n\r\n[toggle title=\"I already have a in-house dialler – can I still trial the system?\" open=\"true or false\" ]\r\nIt’s always a good thing that you are already using a dialer, as you are familiar with this functionality. However, there are some notable limitations with such technology. Your Agents and Administrators will enjoy using BlueCloud – the simplicity and fluidity of the system is addictive. Make sure you get their feedback![/toggle]\r\n\r\n[toggle title=\"Can I make changes to active campaigns while agents are making calls?\" open=\"true or false\" ]\r\nAbsolutely. This makes it possible to make changes at any time during the campaign – even when you are on the road and can only access internet through your phone. Changes will be effected immediately through our powerful back end.[/toggle]\r\n\r\n[toggle title=\"How quickly can I get started?\" open=\"true or false\" ]\r\nAs BlueCloud does not require any special infrastructure or equipment on your end, this can be done very quickly. Depending on the number of agents you wish to enable, set-up can be done as early as the same day if required.[/toggle]\r\n\r\n[toggle title=\"How will you charge me?\" open=\"true or false\" ]\r\nBlueCloud is a pay-as-you-go service with no contracts and no up front hardware investments required. You will pay a small set up fee to get started and will then pay in advance per seat/month. Payment can be made using a credit card (VISA, MasterCard or Amex) or via direct debit. You will be notified by email when credit is low so you can top up your account.[/toggle]\r\n\r\n[toggle title=\"What do I need to do to get started?\" open=\"true or false\" ]\r\nBlueCloud is a cloud based application, hence there is no need for any special hardware on your end. All that is required is an internet enabled computer with a headset for each agent – you don’t even need your telephone system anymore. Does not get much simpler than that.[/toggle]\r\n\r\n[toggle title=\"Why BlueCloud? I already have a system in place.\" open=\"true or false\" ]\r\nAsk yourself these questions….\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><em>Does my system allow me to set up and run a new campaign in less than 15 minutes?</em></li>\r\n	<li><em>Could I be spending too much on technology</em></li>\r\n	<li>Am I in a Contract? What if have a slow month/year?</li>\r\n	<li>Do I pay for Administrator access?</li>\r\n	<li>Do I pay for support? Service Agreements?</li>\r\n	<li><em id=\"__mceDel\"><em id=\"__mceDel\"></em></em><em id=\"__mceDel\"><em id=\"__mceDel\">Do I pay extra for basic features such as recording?</em></em></li>\r\n	<li><em id=\"__mceDel\"><em id=\"__mceDel\"></em></em><em id=\"__mceDel\"><em id=\"__mceDel\">Do I have instant email features as well as video email?</em></em></li>\r\n	<li><em id=\"__mceDel\"><em id=\"__mceDel\"></em></em><em id=\"__mceDel\"><em id=\"__mceDel\">Does my system give me access the cheapest VoIP price plans in the industry?</em></em></li>\r\n	<li><em id=\"__mceDel\"><em id=\"__mceDel\"></em></em><em id=\"__mceDel\"><em id=\"__mceDel\">Am I able to add home based agents and track them the same way as the office based agents?</em></em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\nWe think it may be time for you to review your technology. Call us on 1800 234 350 today.[/toggle]','FAQ','','inherit','closed','open','','56-revision-16','','','2013-06-18 01:48:32','2013-06-18 01:48:32','',56,'http://localhost:8080/restorewp/56-revision-16/',0,'revision','',0),(1480,5,'2013-06-20 12:47:16','2013-06-20 02:47:16','It has never been easier to employ home based agents for your team or even running a virtual call centre where all agents are working from home. Technology is the key enabler here, as cloud solutions are becoming more mainstream. There is now full transparency of all calls made, calls can be recorded and reports are easily available for management. BlueCloud is designed to work seamlessly with home based staff, and would give you an opportunity to have agents accessing the system from anywhere.\r\n\r\nA number of studies have shown that productivity and reductions in staff turnover often follow when staff are given options to work from home, but I won\'t bore you with statistics on this. However, there keep the 4 reasons in mind of you are considering this for your organisation:\r\n\r\n<strong>1. Cost savings</strong>\r\n\r\nDepending on how you manage your home based team there are a few obvious areas for you to save:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"line-height: 13px;\">You can get by with a smaller office (and with far less infrastructure)</span></li>\r\n	<li>Salaries are often far lower in remote areas compared to the main city centres.</li>\r\n	<li>You can have a \"bring your own device\" policy, which means you will not even need to purchase computers for the agents.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>2. Increased Flexibility</strong>\r\n\r\nWorking from home is not just a flexible arrangement for the staff, but for you as an operator this means you can scale up and down much more in line with your changing needs. While some staff may still be employed in a full time basis, you could also have a whole \"army\" of freelancers you could call in when required. You could also easily make changes to the types of agents you employ (age, location etc.).\r\n\r\nThe above mentioned cost savings will also give you far less flexibility to move with the market opportunities in terms of the types of work you and your team are doing.\r\n\r\n<strong>3. Increased Productivity</strong>\r\n\r\nHappy agents will increase your productivity significantly. They will no longer be stuck in traffic or because their spouse forgot to pick the kids up from school. This productivity boost will be visible on your bottom line at the end of each month.\r\n\r\n<strong>4. Higher staff satisfaction</strong>\r\n\r\nNo other industry comes close to the turnover rates we see in the contact centre industry. 40% for full time staff in Australia in 2010. This is extremely high, and suggests that very few see this as a career path. However, you could dramatically reduce turnover by offering options to work from home (and other actions that would increase satisfaction levels). This would be especially true for part time staff (as travel time may be an even greater issue).\r\n\r\nTechnology is not the only thing that needs to be in place to run an effective organisation working from home, but it is the key enabler.\r\n\r\nTalk to us if you are considering home based agents, or if you are already using them. We can in any case help you make this decision simple for you.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','4 reasons why you should consider home based agents','','publish','closed','open','','4-reasons-why-you-should-consider-home-based-agents','','','2013-06-20 12:48:07','2013-06-20 02:48:07','',0,'http://localhost:8080/restorewp/?p=1480',0,'post','',0),(1477,5,'2013-06-18 13:17:13','2013-06-18 13:17:13','[pricing-table col=\"4\"]\r\n\r\n[plan name=\"Test\" link=\"\" linkname=\"Test\" price=\"Test\" per=\"Test\"]\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Multi Function Dialer</li>\r\n	<li>Inbound Support</li>\r\n	<li>Remote Access (any device)</li>\r\n	<li>Advanced Script Module</li>\r\n	<li>Project Management Module</li>\r\n	<li>Advanced Reporting Module</li>\r\n	<li>Call Recording</li>\